<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.7.3">
<l>maccoṭu māḷikai yēṟi mātarkaḷ tammiṭam pukku</l>
<l>kaccoṭu paṭṭaik kiḻittuk kāmpu tukilavai kīṟi</l>
<l>niccalum tīmaikaḷ ceyvāy nīḷtiru vēṅkaṭat tentāy.</l>
<l>paccait tamaṉakat tōṭu pātirip pūccūṭṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are constantly up to no good,</l>
<l rend="indent">climbing the upper story of the mansions,</l>
<l rend="indent">entering the  apartments of the ladies,</l>
<l rend="indent">tearing at the lace borders of [their] girdles,</l>
<l rend="indent">and rending those fine, silk clothes.</l>
<l>My father of high, holy Vēṅkaṭam!</l>
<l>Come so that [I can] adorn [you] with verdant southernwood</l>
<l>and trumpet flower blossoms.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
